#15166
Within Wayreth Forest~
An unnatural silence fills the air here.  No woodland creatures can be
seen or heard, yet the air itself seems to hum with energy.  Stretching in
every direction, row upon row of tall, majestic trees in full spring bloom
seem to whisper to one another.  Time quickly loses any meaning within this
magical woodland, and it becomes hard to tell whether one has been wandering
for hours or days.  Created long ago to ward off any unwelcome visitors, the
Forest of Wayreth stands silent vigil over those foolhardy enough to seek
the Conclave uninvited.  
~
